The [[File:Spreadsheet_SplitCell.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet SplitCell''' tool splits a previously merged cell.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select a [[Spreadsheet_MergeCells|merged]] cell.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_SplitCell.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_SplitCell|Split cell]]}} button.
